name: Polkadots Rear Seat Sun Shade for Phil & Teds Inline Tandem Buggy
description:
Our quality AUSTRALIAN MADE Sun Shades have been custom designed* & made to fit to Phil & Teds E3, Classic & Sports In Line Buggies.

Features triple layer top panel and UV sun mesh sides to reduce harmful rays but still allow your bub to see out. Also provides protection from light to moderate rain. Folds up small to fit in nappy bag or stow in basket underneath.

Our multi-use sun shade grows with your baby. 
1. Firstly, use as a sun & elements shade for the newborn (covers the gap below the handlebar) when the main seat is in lie-flat mode.
2. Then, when you have 2 Toddlers (toddler seat attached to rear of buggy), use as a rear seat sun shade.

Available in a range of fabrics to coordinate with your Phil & Ted's Buggy.

*Registered Design Patent

Shipping 
Australian Customers: Orders processed & shipped within 72hours via Registered Post. 
USA Customers: Orders processed & shipped within 5 days. Shipping via Registered Post International & includes insurance. Buyer's responsibility to pay for any import duty/ taxes that apply.
